# starlight-versions writes frozen snapshots of prior major docs under
# website/src/content/docs/<major>/ (e.g. 2.0/) plus a versions/*.json sidebar
# snapshot. These are generated plugin output, not hand-authored — leave them
# exactly as emitted instead of reformatting them. The current/latest docs at
# website/src/content/docs/ (and everything else) stay prettier-formatted.
website/src/content/docs/[0-9]*/**
website/src/content/versions/*.json
